<plot>Deciding to prove that having a maid is a waste of money (his), Edgar bets his brother-in-law that he can clean the house unaided in three hours. He floods the kitchen while washing the dishes, slips on the linoleum while mopping, and breaks the vacuum cleaner and the furniture in every room.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?248518</url></doc>
